{"tid":812542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放負","createTime":"2018-09-09T17:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T18:01:59.000Z","uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"123a02763f28daaf3256ef209ba6c1dacf82689a","tid":812542,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"我好攰，好多事煩，好疲累。同時間<br />\n<br />\n鍾意既男仔已經鍾意咗好耐<br />\n好多時候都係不理不睬，但有時又會好似好近咁，近到覺得自己有希望。<br />\n係去到岩岩好覺得自己價值好低，又岩岩好唔想放棄想求佢愛我既地步。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己毫不特別既普通人，而且係負能向。<br />\n我無咩地方吸引佢，我知。<br />\n<br />\n鍾意咁耐既時間，有時會好開心。好開心佢對我好，就算係好普通既小事。又或者FF同佢拍拖結婚旅行生仔。但結果還是傷心比開心多。例如好冷漠唔理我既時候，已讀我既時候，講說話hurt我既時候。如果佢真心愛我，會捨得hold住我咁耐，要我唔開心咁耐咩？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己好卑微<br />\n可唔可以處決我，話俾我知我永遠都無希望"},{"pid":"87ea7e5389fb4bd3e7580d73cec00b13147449f4","tid":812542,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"你永遠都無希望㗎啦 收皮啦"},{"pid":"08eb11fc590b967d0d64982c59a4c7f364320895","tid":812542,"uid":112390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:01:46.000Z","msg":"請講"},{"pid":"026c9f3e9c9fb1e957dfbcefff112d6dd7e8458e","tid":812542,"uid":207426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f28ed66f1144be46c6da8b0d964297edf8e1299b","tid":812542,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87ea7e5389fb4bd3e7580d73cec00b13147449f4","tid":812542,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"你永遠都無希望㗎啦 收皮啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dcef462b7ec6892d70f88d14e149642f1ddea0","tid":812542,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08eb11fc590b967d0d64982c59a4c7f364320895","tid":812542,"uid":112390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:01:46.000Z","msg":"請講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:09